About
A Simple Home Life is a Happy Home Life
Nestled in the heart of St. Petersburg, FL, Pelican Palms Village is a remarkably convenient location for your place in the sun. Whether you plan to stay year-round or for a winter get away, you’ll find great restaurants, retail outlets, a post office, drug store and more located right across the street from our grounds.
A Simple Home Life is a Happy Home Life
Nestled in the heart of St. Petersburg, FL, Pelican Palms Village is a remarkably convenient location for your place in the sun. Whether you plan to stay year-round or for a winter get away, you’ll find great restaurants, retail outlets, a post office, drug store and more located right across the street from our grounds.
Enjoy Your Retirement Years Burden-Free
Our peaceful mobile home community has 286 pads of which 85% are currently leased. Of these homes, 64% are single wide, 31% are double wide and all include carports. For visiting friends and families, we have 5% RV sites.
Enjoy our convenient on-site amenities including a heated swimming pool and hot tub, a community clubhouse, exercise classes and special events. And, when it’s time to get out and explore, you’ll find plenty of world-class attractions, top events and outdoor adventures throughout St. Petersburg and nearby Tampa!
